fb \(
fb {d \over dx} (log_{b} x) = {1 \over {x \ln b}}, \hbox{for}
fb \, x > 0
fb \)
fb 
fb and
fb 
fb \(
fb {d \over dx}(log_{b}|x|) = {1 \over {x \ln b}}, \hbox{for}
fb \, x \ne 0
fb \)
fb 

